list.comment: - CHG: Version bump for bugfix release.

task.summary: Default task
- CHG: Changed the way reps are handled. There's now a dedicated `rep` column in the phenotypedata table.
- CHG: Improved performance of the attribute data import. - CHG: Smaller changes to the genotype import.
- CHG: Added explicit HDF5 output paths to genotypic importers.
- CHG: Added explicit HDF5 output paths to genotypic importers.
- ADD: Added Hapmap importer. - CHG: Massively restructured the code to simplify things.
- ADD: Added Hapmap importer. - CHG: Massively restructured the code to simplify things.
- DEL: Removed unnecessary dummy code.
- FIX: Fixed dependency inconsistency.
- FIX: Fixed import issues when no map is available.
- FIX: Fixed hapmap import with inconsistent map information.
- ADD: Added missing license file.
- CHG: Changed the genotypic data importer to also create a transposed HDF5 file for better performance when exporting to Hapmap.
- CHG: FJ importer: Only import map if there are chromosome and position values on it.
- CHG: Updated dependencies.
- FIX: Fixed an issue where importing genotypic data without a map wasn't possible.
- FIX: Removed dummy map creation when there are no chromosome and position definitions.
- CHG: Updated to latest database scheme.
- FIX: Fixed an issue with HDF5 file creation where the source file doesn't contain any map information.
- CHG: Updated dependencies.
- CHG: Changed pedigree importer to support datasets.
- CHG: Updated dependencies.
- CHG: Updated dependencies. - ADD: Added block, latitude, longitude and elevation columns to trials data importer.

- FIX: Fixed issues with missing trials block info. - FIX: Fixed issues with germplasm MCPD pedigree importer (missing dataset). - CHG: Updated METADATA parsing to include new rows. - CHG: Updated COLLABORATORS parsing to include new columns. - CHG: Renamed climate template to environmental data template. This required updating sheet names.
- CHG: Minimal code cleanup.
- CHG: Updated dependencies. - FIX: Fixed small bug with trials data import.

- ADD: Added new parameter to all importers that provides the original filename. - ADD: Added creation of file resource for original file. - ADD: Added code that links the new file resource to a potentially created dataset.
- CHG: Updated importers to pull parameters from the database rather than the commandline. - CHG: Updated importers to write job status back to database.
- ADD: Added bulk image uploader.
- CHG: Set job running in the database once the code starts executing.
- FIX: Fixed dataset import backup for images where only the template, not the zip was backed up.
- CHG: Updated MCPD importer to use new MCPD table.

- FIX: Fixed the catch-all exception handling which didn't store feedback to the database. - FIX: Fixed a bug where institution import from the MCPD would fail if no institution code was available. - FIX: Added MCPD fields that are also stored elsewhere to the mcpd table. -
- CHG: Updated dependencies. - CHG: Version bump to 4.4.0.
- CHG: Fixed issues with MCPD importer only supporting a single duplicate institution.
- FIX: Fixed potential issues with germplasm name matching.
- CHG: Updated dependencies.
- CHG: Updated dependencies.

- FIX: Fixed issues with Excel genotype importer. It wasn't updating the flat file importer internally. - CHG: Removed compound importer as it has been merged with trials data templates. - CHG: Version bump to 4.4.2.
- CHG: Version bump to 4.4.2.
- CHG: Updates to accommodate row/column index for phenotypic data.
- ADD: Added importer for trials data shapefiles. - ADD: Added WARNING status codes in addition to just ERROR
- ADD: Added import job stat counts. - CHG: Changed the experiment that will be created by dataset imports to use a generic experiment. Can be re-assigned in the UI later.
- ADD: Added a way to support import of genotypic data straight from the command line without going through the Germinate API.
- CHG: Dependency update.
- CHG: Dependency update.
- ADD: Set fileResourceId in data import job stats.
- ADD: Added trials data check for Rep column values. They are now required.
- CHG: Dependency update to support Tomcat 10.1. - ADD: Added support for transposed Excel data import.
- CHG: Slightly changed how trait definitions are matched against the database by restricting the fields that are checked to a minimum.
